description: Description The listing price is for 5 piece / 1 card battery only. The Sony 379 Coin Cell is most often used as a watch battery replacement. Button battery cells can also be used in other electronic devices such as keyless remote entry systems for cars and homes, in hand-held electronic devices, and as batteries in caluclators, photo cameras, audio books, games, toys, and more. Has a shelf life of 5+ years. Equivalent Battery Types: AWI S56, Beltone B379L, Bulova 618, Citizen 280-59, Duracell D379, 379B, Eveready 379, Gold Peak GP79, I.E.C.
